13:45.284 --> 13:46.326
<i>Nu, nu.</i>

13:46.994 --> 13:47.995
<i>Sì.</i>

13:49.329 --> 13:50.455
<i>Nu, nu, nu, nu.</i>

13:50.455 --> 13:52.374
Nu așa de repede acum.

13:52.749 --> 13:53.959
<i>Nu. Nu, nu.</i>

13:55.377 --> 13:57.129
Rana ta...

13:57.129 --> 13:59.423
